name: Modern Organic Forms /// Black and White Block Print
description:
This is an original hand carved and hand printed block print. It features a playful and organic forms. This great print makes a fun statement. It would look great in any space and works well in either a modern frame or a more rustic frame.

ink color: black
paper: 100 lb. bristol paper
medium: water based ink
Dimensions of print: 5" x 7" (an additional 1/2" - 1" border will surround the print)

+ Slight variations from print to print will occur*

+ I try to make sure that the colors represented are as close to true as possible, but please remember that colors may differ slightly from what your monitor displays.

+ Rights to paintings and other artwork do not transfer with the sale of an item.

It is signed and dated by the artist and the print will come in a clear cellophane envelope and will be shipped flat.

THANK YOU for visiting my shop and I hope you find something unique and beautiful.
